      "body": "A REDACTED is a purpose-built database system designed to store, index, and query high-dimensional vector embeddings efficiently. Vector databases power modern semantic search, recommendation engines, and retrieval-augmented generation pipelines. Unlike traditional relational databases, a REDACTED organises data around approximate nearest-neighbour (ANN) indices so that similarity queries over millions of vectors complete in milliseconds.",
